---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout
  title="Compact Industries — Customer Story — Formic"
  description="Compact Industries, a 1963-founded Chicago packaging specialist serving Fortune 500 clients, deployed a Formic collaborative palletizer — 'Rosie' — running 720 cases an hour to combat labor shortages."
  ogTitle="Compact Industries — Formic Customer Story"
  ogDescription="720 cases/hour · 6 cycles/min · second system in a month"
>
  <link rel="canonical" href="https://formic.co/stories/compact-industries" slot="head" />

<div class="detail-bc">
  <a href="/">Home</a><span class="sep">/</span><a href="/stories">Customer Stories</a><span class="sep">/</span>Compact Industries
</div>

<section class="detail-hero">
  <div class="si">
    <div class="slabel" style="color:var(--orange)">Customer Story · Compact Industries</div>
    <h1 style="font-size:clamp(32px,3.8vw,56px)">Compact Industries Partners with Formic to Combat Labor Shortages and Accelerate Factory Productivity</h1>
    <p class="lede">Formic helped revolutionize Compact Industries' production process, jumpstarting their automation journey. In record time, the 1963-founded food and beverage packaging specialist went from delivery to palletization with a collaborative robotic system — ushering in unprecedented productivity and efficiency gains.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block dark">
  <div class="detail-video wide">
    <div class="detail-video-frame">
      <img src="/stories/compact-industries-hero.jpg" alt="Compact Industries collaborative palletizing system" />
      <span class="dv-cap">Compact Industries · Chicago, Illinois</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block white" style="padding:64px 0 0">
  <div class="si" style="max-width:1280px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 80px">
    <div class="db-tag">At a glance</div>
    <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(150px,1fr));gap:1px;background:var(--lgrey);border:1px solid var(--lgrey);margin-top:14px">
      <div style="background:var(--white);padding:18px 20px"><div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:9px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--mgrey);margin-bottom:6px">Founded</div><div style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:17px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:-.01em;color:var(--black)">1963</div></div>
      <div style="background:var(--white);padding:18px 20px"><div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:9px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--mgrey);margin-bottom:6px">Location</div><div style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:17px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:-.01em;color:var(--black)">Chicago, Illinois</div></div>
      <div style="background:var(--white);padding:18px 20px"><div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:9px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--mgrey);margin-bottom:6px">Industry</div><div style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:17px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:-.01em;color:var(--black)">Food & beverage packaging</div></div>
      <div style="background:var(--white);padding:18px 20px"><div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:9px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--mgrey);margin-bottom:6px">Clients</div><div style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:17px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:-.01em;color:var(--black)">Fortune 500 brands</div></div>
      <div style="background:var(--white);padding:18px 20px"><div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:9px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--mgrey);margin-bottom:6px">The robot</div><div style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:17px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:-.01em;color:var(--black)">Nicknamed "Rosie"</div></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block white">
  <div class="db-grid">
    <div class="db-text">
      <div class="db-tag">01 — The Challenge</div>
      <h2>Quality demands consistency. <em>Labor wouldn't cooperate.</em></h2>
      <p>Compact Industries, a Chicago-based specialty packager serving Fortune 500 clients, names low labor retention as its single biggest challenge — against an industry backdrop where 8 in 10 manufacturing executives reported labor shortages and 877,250 manufacturing jobs sat open that year.</p>
      <ul class="feats">
        <li>Fortune 500 clients, a high quality and consistency bar</li>
        <li>Low labor retention the biggest challenge</li>
        <li>877,250 open manufacturing jobs that year</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="db-img"><img src="/stories/compact-industries-2.jpg" alt="Compact Industries mobile palletizing robot" loading="lazy"/><span class="img-cap">Mobile palletizing · "Rosie"</span></div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block lgrey">
  <div class="db-grid flip">
    <div class="db-img"><img src="/Talos-0095.jpg" alt="Formic collaborative palletizing system" loading="lazy"/><span class="img-cap">720 cases / hour</span></div>
    <div class="db-text">
      <div class="db-tag">02 — The Solution</div>
      <h2>Meet "Rosie", <em>720 cases an hour</em>.</h2>
      <p>With partner SourceLink Solutions, Formic deployed a Yaskawa collaborative robot as a mobile palletizing system: 35 lbs per pick, 6 cycles per minute, 720 cases per hour, five minutes to switch tasks, and about an hour to add new products. The team nicknamed it "Rosie" — and ordered a second system within a month.</p>
      <ul class="feats">
        <li>35 lbs per pick, 6 cycles/min, 720 cases/hour</li>
        <li>5 minutes to switch tasks, ~1 hour to add products</li>
        <li>Second system ordered within a month</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block white" style="padding:88px 80px">
  <div class="si" style="max-width:900px;margin:0 auto;padding:0">
    <div class="pull-quote">
      <blockquote>"What attracted me to Formic was the low risk... I felt very confident with Formic. The whole process was so seamless, and this quality of service didn't happen when we tried to automate on our own."</blockquote>
      <cite>Rich Moldovan · Engineering Manager, Compact Industries</cite>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block dark">
  <div class="si" style="max-width:1280px;margin:0 auto;padding:80px;text-align:center">
    <div class="db-tag" style="justify-content:center">03 — The Outcome</div>
    <h2 style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:clamp(40px,5vw,72px);font-weight:500;letter-spacing:-.02em;line-height:1;color:var(--white);margin:18px 0 56px">From delivery to palletization, <em style="color:var(--orange);font-style:normal">in record time.</em></h2>
    <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:1px;background:rgba(255,255,255,.1)">
      <div style="background:var(--black);padding:36px 24px"><div style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:48px;font-weight:500;color:var(--orange);line-height:1">720</div><div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10px;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(240,245,241,.55);margin-top:12px">Cases per hour</div></div>
      <div style="background:var(--black);padding:36px 24px"><div style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:48px;font-weight:500;color:var(--orange);line-height:1">6</div><div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10px;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(240,245,241,.55);margin-top:12px">Cycles per minute</div></div>
      <div style="background:var(--black);padding:36px 24px"><div style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:48px;font-weight:500;color:var(--orange);line-height:1">5 min</div><div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10px;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(240,245,241,.55);margin-top:12px">To switch tasks</div></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-cta">
  <h2>Accelerate your <em>factory</em>.</h2>
  <div class="btn-row">
    <a href="mailto:sales@formic.co" class="btn-ctadark">Get Started</a>
    <a href="/stories" class="btn-ctawh">More Customer Stories</a>
  </div>
</section>
</Layout>
